Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Everywhere Kamala Harris has gone she has been followed by failure and suffering. As just one example, when she was put in charge of the Border, the “Border Czar,” it became the worst and most dangerous Border anywhere in the World! Sheriff Mike Boudreaux of the California State Sheriff’s Association, was used in a Kamala ad, but says he supports TRUMP - Manipulation of everything!
